.container
  .card.shadow
    .card-header
      %h1.h3
        About Corsego
    .card-body
      %h4 Why Corsego?
      %p
        Most people know something worth teaching. Corsego gives you the tools to package that knowledge into a course and get it in front of students who want to learn it — no middleman, no gatekeepers.
      %p
        If you're here to learn, you get straightforward access to courses made by people who actually do the work. No algorithms deciding what you should watch next. Pick a course, enroll, and it's yours forever.

      %hr
      %h4 Teach and earn
      %p
        If you can explain something well, you can build a course on Corsego. The course builder lets you organize chapters and lessons, add video and rich text content, set your own price, and start earning when students enroll.
      %ul
        %li Structure your course with chapters and lessons
        %li Embed videos, write rich text content, attach files
        %li Set your price — you decide what your course is worth
        %li Get paid directly through Stripe when students enroll

      %hr
      %h4 Learn on your terms
      %p
        Every enrollment comes with lifetime access. No recurring fees, no expiration dates. Work through the material at whatever pace suits you, and download a certificate when you're done.
      %ul
        %li Lifetime access to every course you enroll in
        %li Track your progress lesson by lesson
        %li Earn a certificate of completion
        %li Leave reviews to help other students choose

    .card-footer
      Questions?
